title: [1508521049] Best Italian Restaurant: Casamia Big Test - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Italian restaurant, Casamia, face their toughest challenge yet when they serve to Gordon Ramsay's esteemed guests in his Kitchen.

Gordon Ramsay in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title.
